Feisty Doge

While not as well-known as some Doge images, this photo of the Shiba Inu “Kabosu” was taken by her owner Atsuko Sato on February 13th, 2010. Sato shared this image and several others to her personal blog under the title “Taking a walk with Kabosu-chan,” which went on to become one of the most iconic memes of all time.
